=== DIAGNOSTIC APPLICATION ===

To recognize I-Tube health:
1. Where does it choke? (bottleneck too narrow)
2. Where does it flood? (bottleneck too wide)
3. What gets lost in left funnel? (compression cost)
4. How much diversity can you compress? (capacity)
5. How do you expand without diluting? (right funnel)

Optimal: flow with transformation. Pathological: choking or flooding.

